.TH GURU 1 2025-07-16 "Guru Package Manager"

.SH NAME

\fBguru\fR \- package format for Guru Package Manager

.SH SYNOPSIS

The following relative paths have meaning within a Guru package:

\fIpkg\fR/apt, \fIpkg\fR/bin/, \fIpkg\fR/fs/, \fIpkg\fR/group, \fIpkg\fR/lib/,
\fIpkg\fR/man/, \fIpkg\fR/passwd, \fIpkg\fR/share/, \fIpkg\fR/version

.SH DESCRIPTION

This article describes the layout of a Guru package.  Guru packages can be
installed using the \fBguru\fR(1) command.

